reverseR 0.1 (16-02-2017)

* first package version

reverseR 0.2 (10-05-2022)

* many small changes in existing functions
* added 'bootLM' (bootstrap) and 'jackLM' (jackknife)
* added PNAS 2015 dataset
* removed 'shinyInfl' as 'lmInfl' suffices for the analysis
* added 'rpLM' for estimating the replication probability of a (univariate) linear model
* removed 'simInfl', a not really needed function
* added 'pcomp' for testing 7 robust methods on a linear model
* simplified 'regionInfl'

